official_title: Expressing the sense of the Congress respecting the 80th anniversary of the Anti-Defamation League.
subjects: Civil rights and liberties, minority issues

summary.text: Congratulates the Anti-Defamation League on its 80th anniversary and commends it for effectively pursuing the goal of promoting greater tolerance throughout the world.
